# Normalize all text files to LF in the repository, regardless of a
# contributor's core.autocrlf setting. Without this, core.autocrlf=true rewrites
# checked-out files to CRLF, which then show as "modified" and emit
# "LF will be replaced by CRLF" warnings on every git operation — pure noise
# that also churns the generated docs. `text=auto eol=lf` pins the working-tree
# and committed line endings to LF for everything git detects as text.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary types: never touch line endings.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
